{
  "stem": "1929.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a lot of Russian-- Ukrainians, which were like Russians with their horses, and they would do all kinds of antics on their horses.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would get drunk, and they would be galloping around the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't remember really much danger to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I just remember kind of being free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I know that-- the only one I can remember from Bugaj was my, my cousin, and my cousin Anna and her two little girls.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember visiting them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were in a different building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the other significant thing that happened there to me was that my brother and a friend of his were engaged in smuggling in food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A lot of the transports that used to come in bringing in raw material, he was able to-- they were able to smuggle in bread and potatoes and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I just wanted to be of some use.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I always bugged him to help me, that I should be part of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So, so he finally let me-- let me go with him where they were going to meet this wagon that was coming in, and we would carry some potatoes and stuff.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we were there-- him, myself, and somebody else-- this Fischer, this, this owner, he owned the-- he was also part of things, the Gestapo-- who owned this factory-- they hid some place and I was trying to hid.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyway, I got caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He caught me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had his dog with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He takes out his revolver, and he says-- he takes out a bullet and he shows, see this bullet here?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to-- this is what is going to go through your head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
